76561198024845522,Recommended,209670,8459231,"Posted: 31 December, 2013",all,Inviktys,"Great Game!It is completely different from what the trailer depicts ( I suggest watching a few ""let's Play!"" videos) but the gem that is underneath is beautiful...and a little flawed.The Game is a 2D RTS/Platformer/Action hybrid where you take the reigns of a disembodied brain whose goal is to become rich by claiming all of the gold mining sites on the planet's surface.Now...let me tell you the campaign is kind of dull (or at least I found it to be) but the varied skirmishes more than make up for it.The hilarity of combat is what makes this game shine, enemy drop ships landing on the planet's surface? take your trusty rocket launcher and blow it out of the sky, but beware! loose engine pods have a tendency to zoom off in random directions acting as a unstoppable battering ram. If you are successful in combat, holding the breach from waves of enemies, do not be surprised when the climb the mountain of corpses and attack from above, or mine below the surface, digging the ground from underneath you.What makes this game even better are the loads of mods found on theDATAREALMS.COMforums, adding factions and hilarious weapons to the gameplay.Catch it on sale and do not miss this. The company (and man) who made this game did an amazing job so show your support!"
