,Recommended,209670,28828862,"Posted: 30 December, 2016",all,Corban,"Overall a kind of ""meh"" game. It has a lot of potential to be fun, but the issue is how opaque a lot of the features are. The tutorial covers the absolute bare minimum of moving around and shooting, and the basic objectives, but does not cover anything regarding the career mode such as base building or even turn structure. Get it while it's on sale. At $3, I definitely feel I got my money's worth, but it's not quite got enough polish to shell out the full asking price."
